Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.92,0:03:05.12,Defaultint,Phone,0,0,0,,Prosím, vrať se!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.62,0:03:09.46,Default,Souta narration,0,0,0,,Jinak to nejde...
